Dumb little projects:

Caesar Cipher.py
  Run python File
  Enter your String
  Enter your Shift Value (Password)
  Enter your Method

Long Alphabet Cipher.py
  Run python File
  Enter your String
  Application returns the string where every character is replaced with the longest word beginning with that letter

Extended Cipher.py
  Run the python file
  Enter your string
  Enter your Caesar Password
  Enter your XOR Password
  Recieve your new String
